data.title: Unlock scooter from app to start/resume trip
data.sub_title: Swipe to unlock the scooter & start or resume your trip. Press self start button to ride.

data.title: Open the trunk for helmet
data.sub_title: Use app to open the trunk & take the helmet. Keep it back after your ride :)

data.title: Turn engine off by pressing button on Scooter
data.sub_title: Use this to turn engine off at traffic signals while you are waiting.

data.title: End your trip from app
data.sub_title: Press End trip on the app & share your feedback to end your booking.
